name: 3d_face_mask_nose_wire
description:
Handmade face mask, 3D style (one size), Washable, Made with 2 layers of cotton, 
Soft elastic ear loops, Comfortable design, How to wash: Machine washable at 30 degrees in a laundry bag / pillow case or wash with 
soapy water. Rinse thoroughly and air dry. Do not tumble dry. Please note these are not of medical grade. Please wash before use.
